item.title: Ice Queen Nails Spa
item.description: The cold princess Elsa also looks after her nails. Your task is to give the girl a quality manicure. Use various tools for this - a file, tweezers. Hints will help you cope with the processing process. And then choose the right varnish and apply it on the nails.
